name: Washi Wheel
description:
**International Customer:  please email us for a shipping quote before completing your order.  Thank you!**

Our new washi wheel is a great way to keep your favorites close at hand and is super cute and colorful sitting on your workspace.    

Each wheel will hold up to 72 rolls of washi tape and our design makes it quick & easy to change out/rearrange the rolls and doesn't take up a lot of space!  

Measures 6 1/4" wide x 9 1/2" long x 8" tall.  

Leave it natural, paint or stain it to match your décor!  

Each washi wheel is handmade right here in the US!

name: 3x4 Storage Box
description:
**International Customer:  please email us for a shipping quote before completing your order.  Thank you!**

This handmade wooden box is perfect for storing Project Life cards (will hold up to 500 cards), embellishments, die cuts or any other small crafting supplies. 

All of our boxes are handmade from various types of wood, so no two boxes will be exactly alike, but that's what makes them unique!  

You can leave them natural or paint/decorate them to match your decor!  Be sure to check out Amy Tan's blog to see how she decorated hers!  

Measures 4" wide x 5 1/2" long x 3 1/4" tall. 

Proudly made in the USA.

name: Handmade Wooden Toy Train
description:
This quality, handmade toy train is the perfect gift for any child!   

We leave each train natural so kids are free to paint or decorate it any way they choose!

We only have a limited number available, so get yours in time for Christmas!

name: Washi tape box
description:
**International Customer:  please email us for a shipping quote before completing your order.  Thank you!**

This handmade wooden box is perfect for storing up to 24 rolls of your favorite washi tape!  Easy to remove dowel rods make it easy to add/remove washi rolls.  

The boxes are also stackable!!  

Each box is handmade from various types of wood, so no two holders will be exactly alike, but that's what makes them unique!  

You can leave it natural, stain or paint or decorate it to match your décor.  

Be sure to check out Amy Tan's, Ali Edwards', Ann-Marie Morris and Pam Garrison's blogs to see how each of them have used our washi box!    

Measures 6" wide x 8 1/2" long x 2 1/4" tall. 

Handmade in the USA.
